									</div>
									<div class="checklist-note">
										<small>üí° Copy the folder link above and open in your Chrome, then click "New" ‚Üí "Google Sheets"</small>
									</div>
								</div>
								
								<div class="checklist-section">
									<h5>üí¨ DISCORD</h5>
